Owir Jehu mondo obed ruodh Israel


1  Elisha janabi noluongo achiel kuom jonabi, mowachone niya, “Ng’wan lepi, idhi Ramoth-gilead gi puga mar morni. 
2  Kichopo, dwar Jehu wuod Jehoshafat ma wuod Nimshi. Kisetundo kama entie, to gole kuom jolweny wetene, kendo itere e ot maiye. 
3  Eka ikaw puga mar mo, iol e wiye, kikone ni Ruoth Nyasaye owachone ni oseyiere mondo obed ruodh Israel. Ka isewacho kamano, to yaw dhoot iring ia. Kik ideki!”


4  Omiyo janabi ma rawerano nodhi Ramoth-gilead, 
5  monwang’o jodong lweny ka nie bura. Nowacho niya, “Jaduong’, adwaro loso kodi.” Jehu nopenje niya, “En ng’a ma idwaro losogo kuomwa?” Nodwoke ni, “Mana in, jaduong’” 
6  

Mi Jehu noa malo, modonjo e ot. Eka janabino noolo mo e wiye, kawachone ni Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel owacho niya, “Aseyieri mondo ibed ruodh Israel. 
7  Inineg dhood Ahab ma ruodhu, mondo ochulgo kuor kuom Jezebel nikech nochuero remb jotichna ma jonabi, kod jotichna mamoko duto. 
8  Dhood Ahab duto norum! Anatiek jo-Ahab machwo duto, ma onge kata achiel ma nodong’ e Israel. 
9  Analok dhoode mondo ochal gi dhood Jeroboam wuod Nebat, kendo machal gi dhood Baasha wuod Ahija. 
10  

Guogi nocham Jezebel e piny Jezreel, kendo onge ng’ama nokonye.” Eka janabino noyawo dhoot, moringo.


11  Kane Jehu owuok, modok ir jodong ruodhe, ne gipenje niya, “Ere wach? Janekono nobiro iri nang’o?” Nodwokogi niya, “Ung’eyo kaka ng’atno wuoyo!” 
12  To ne gikwere ni, “Mano miriambo! Wachnwa awacha adiera.” Nodwokogi kendo niya, “Nonyisa ni Ruoth Nyasaye owacho ni oseyiera mondo abed ruodh Israel.” 
13  Mi jogo duto nopedho lepgi aruya ewi raidhi, mondo Jehu obedie. Eka ne gigoyo tung’ ka gikok niya, “Jehu e ruoth!”

Jehu onego Joram, ruodh Israel


14  Kamano e kaka Jehu wuod Jehoshsfat ma wuod Nimshi nochako piem gi Joram, mondo ogol e tich ruoth. 
15  Jehu nowacho ni jodong lweny wetene niya, “Ka parou chal kamano, to kara neuru ni ng’ato ok owuok e dala ka, ma diter wach Jezreel.” 
16  Eka Jehu noidho gache, modhi Jezreel, nimar Joram ne ni kuno. To Ahazia ruodh Juda bende ne ni kuno, ka wendo Joram. (Ruoth Joram ne ni Jezreel mondo ochang kuom hinyruok mane oyudo e lwet jo-Aram Ramoth-gilead gi jo-Israel duto, mondo kik Hazael ruodh Aram kaw.)


17  Jarito mane oyudo ochung’ ewi ohinga mar Jezreel noneno Jehu gi joge ka biro, mowacho niya, “Aneno ji moko, ka biro.” Joram nowachone ni, “Or ng’ato gi faras odhi oromnigi, mondo openjgi ka wach ber.” 
18  Omiyo jaidh faras nodhi romonigi, mowachonigi niya, “Ruoth penjo ka wach ber.” To Jehu nodwoke niya, “Wach maber obadhie ang’o? Wichri ilu bang’a.” Jarito mane ni ewi ohinga nochako owacho niya, “Jaote cha osechopo irgi, to ok ane koduogo.” 
19  Eka ruoth nooro jaidh faras machielo, ma bende nowachonigi niya, “Ruoth penjo ka wach ber.” Jehu nodwoke niya, “Wach maber obadhie ang’o? Wichri ilu bang’a.” 
20  Jarito nowacho kendo niya, “Jaoteno osechopo irgi, to en bende ok oduogi. To jariemb gari cha chalo mana gi Jehu wuod Nimshi, nikech oriembo matek ka janeko.”


21  Joram nowacho ni joge mondo oikne gache, mi ne gitimo kamano. Eka Joram ruodh Israel, kod Ahazia ruodh Juda, ne jowuok gi gechegi, ka dhi romo ni Jehu, mi ne giromo kode e puoth Naboth ja-Jezreel. 
22  Kane Joram oneno Jehu, nopenje niya, “Ere kaka wach nyalo bet maber, ka meru Jezebel pod dhi nyime gi timbene mag ndhogruok gi mag jwok?” 
23  Kane Joram owinjo wachno, noloko gache moringo, kowacho ni Ahazia niya, “Ahazia masira ni ka! Jogi jemo!” 
24  To Jehu noywayo asere gi tekone duto, mochwowo otenga Joram, mi asere nopowo e dho chunye, monywowore e gache. 
25  Eka Jehu nowacho ni Bidkar mane jating’ne gilweny niya, “Kawe, ibole e pwoth Naboth ja-Jezreel. Ok ipar gima Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho kuome chieng’ mane wan kodi e gach lweny, kwaluwo bang’ Ahab wuon mare? 
26  

Donge Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho kuome ni, ‘Nyoro aneni kinego Naboth gi yawuote, to abiro chuloni kuor e puodhoni’? Omiyo kawe, ibole e puodhono, mondo wach Ruoth Nyasaye ochop kare.”

