27  Kane ahazia ruodh Juda oneno gima otimore, noringo kochomo Beth-hagan. Jehu nolawe, kawacho niya, “En bende negeuru!” Mi ne gichwowe ka geche idho got Gur, machiegni gi Ibleam. Noringo nyaka Megido, motho kuro. 
28  Joge noting’e e gari nyaka jerusalem, mi giyike but kwerene e dala Daudi.


29  Ahazia nochako bet ruodh Juda e higa mar apar gachiel mar loch Joram wuod Ahab.

Tho mar Jezebel


30  Kane Jehu ochopo Jezreel, Jezebel nowinjo birone, omiyo nowiro wang’e gi mo, kendo oloso yie wiye. Eka nong’icho gie dirisa. 
31  Kane Jehu odonjo e dhorangach, Jezebel nowachone niya, “Ere wach, in Zimri ma janek ruodheni?” 
32  Jehu noting’o wang’e, mong’iyo dirisa kapenjo niya, “Ere ng’ama odokna?” Eka jotich ariyo kata adek nobiro e dirisa, mong’iye. 
33  Jehu nowacho nigi niya, “Dhiruru dhakono piny.” Kamano ne gidhire, mi rembe nokirore e kor ot, kendo farese nonyone. 
34  Jehu nodonjo e ot, mochiemo kendo ometho. Eka nowacho niya, “Dhiuru uyik dhako mokuong’ni nikech en nyar ruoth.” 
35  To kane gidhi mondo giyike, ne ginwang’o mana hanga wiye gi tiendene kod luetene kende. 
36  

Kane gidok nyiso Jehu, nowachonigi niya, “Mano e gima Ruoth Nyasaye nomiyo jatichne Elija ja-Tishbe owacho, kokoro niya, ‘Guogi nocham ringre Jezebel e gweng’ Jezreel; 
37  kendo ringre nochal kaka owuoyo moyar e puothe mag Jezreel, ma onge ng’ato ma nong’e ni, ma e Jezebel.’ ”

